The slammer.
监狱。

163
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:42,200
Yeah, well, I don't blame them.
是啊，我不怪他们。

164
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,760
I wouldn't want to go to the slammer either.
我也不想进监狱。

165
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,360
