现在来看我们的最后一个词。

251
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,120
You may have seen the word fellas.
你可能见过“fellas”这个词。

252
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:48,120
Fellas.
伙计们。

253
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:54,200
So this comes from the word fellow, person, man.
这个词来自“fellow”，意思是人、男人。

254
00:10:54,200 --> 00:11:03,880
But oftentimes in these kind of movies or stories about heists or crimes, the men talk
但在这种关于抢劫或犯罪的电影或故事中，男人们经常

