00:11:03,880 --> 00:11:06,760
to each other using the word fella or fellas.
用“fella”或“fellas”互相称呼。

256
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:08,200
So come on, fellas.
所以，“来吧，伙计们”。

257
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,400
Let's go.
我们走。

258
00:11:09,400 --> 00:11:10,680
That means come on, guys.
意思是“来吧，大家”。

259
00:11:10,680 --> 00:11:11,680
Come on, everyone.
来吧，所有人。

260
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:12,680
Okay.
好的。

261
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,680
Yeah.
是的。

262
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:17,400
So this is always about men, not like a group of women would use this.
所以这总是关于男人的，不像一群女人会用这个词。

263
00:11:17,400 --> 00:11:19,480
And it's something that's a little bit older.
而且这是一个有点老式的说法。

264
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:23,680
We don't really say this like oh, me and my fellas, we're going to go to the store.
我们不会真的说“哦，我和我的伙计们，我们要去商店”。

265
00:11:23,680 --> 00:11:26,200
You would say this more in old time English.
你更可能在老式英语中这么说。

266
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,200
Yeah.
是的。

267
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:31,360
You can see it maybe in some movies when somebody comes up and greets other people, other guys,
你可能会在一些电影中看到，当有人过来问候其他人、其他家伙时，

