It's about the American mafia called Goodfellas.
是关于美国黑帮的，叫《好家伙》。

272
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,200
Very good.
非常好。

273
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:39,320
It's a very famous one.
这是一部非常著名的电影。

274
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:44,160
So it kind of gives you that feeling of an older English like the 1940s to the 1970s.
所以它给人一种老式英语的感觉，比如1940年代到1970年代。

275
00:11:44,160 --> 00:11:45,160
Okay.
好的。

276
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:46,160
Very good.
非常好。

277
00:11:46,160 --> 00:11:47,920
So we've got a lot of things going on in this bank robbery.
所以这次银行抢劫中有很多事情发生。

278
00:11:47,920 --> 00:11:51,960
Why don't we go back, listen to the dialogue one last time and we'll be back in a little
我们为什么不回去，再听一遍对话，然后我们一会儿

279
00:11:51,960 --> 00:12:01,840
bit.
再回来。

280
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:05,320
Alright let's run through this one more time from the top.
好的，让我们从头再过一遍。

281
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:09,840
I will be positioned here across from the bank on this park bench.
我会坐在银行对面的公园长椅上。

282
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,160
Now according to the intel we got from Jimmy.
根据我们从吉米那里得到的情报。

283
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:13,800
Oh, who's Jimmy?
哦，吉米是谁？

284
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:17,240
Geez, Ralph, pay attention, will ya?
天哪，拉尔夫，注意点，好吗？

285
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:18,920
Jimmy's our mole, you know?
吉米是我们的内线，知道吗？

286
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,760
The guy on the inside.
那个内部的人。

287
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:24,640
He's been snooping and passing on the info to us so we can pull this heist off.
他一直在暗中打探并把信息传给我们，这样我们才能完成这次抢劫。

288
00:12:24,640 --> 00:12:28,520
Yeah, Ralph, clean the mothballs out of your ears and listen up.
是啊，拉尔夫，把耳朵里的樟脑丸清干净，好好听着。

289
00:12:28,520 --> 00:12:30,000
This here is important.
这很重要。

290
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:32,960
We don't want to end up back in the slammer, do ya?
我们可不想再回到监狱里，对吧？

291
00:12:32,960 --> 00:12:34,520
Your role is pretty important here.
你的角色在这里相当重要。

292
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:36,080
We're dependent on you, man.
我们全靠你了，老兄。

293
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:39,000
Okay, okay, I'm listening.
好的，好的，我在听。

294
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:40,000
Mothballs.
樟脑丸。

295
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:42,000
Alrighty then.
好的，那么。

296
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,000
Where was I?
我说到哪儿了？

297
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:44,000
Yeah, okay.
是的，好的。

298
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:48,640
So, I'll be on the lookout, sitting here on the bench across from the bank.
所以，我会放哨，坐在银行对面的长椅上。

299
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:52,240
Nobody moves until I give the go-ahead, alright?
在我发出行动信号之前，谁都不许动，明白吗？

300
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,600
And what's the go-ahead, Ralph?
那行动信号是什么，拉尔夫？

301
00:12:54,600 --> 00:13:00,120
You uh, you uh, oh yeah, you'll take off your hat and scratch your head.
你呃，你呃，哦对了，你会摘下帽子挠头。

302
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,120
Right.
对。

303
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:04,640
When I take my hat off and scratch my head, you do what?
当我摘下帽子挠头时，你做什么？

304
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,120
I get in the box.
我进箱子。

305
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:08,040
Right, you get in the box.
对，你进箱子。

306
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:12,800
I'll make sure it's all sealed and then posing as the delivery guy, I'll drop off a special
我会确保箱子封好，然后假扮成送货员，给经理送一个特别的

307
00:13:12,800 --> 00:13:14,680
package for the manager.
包裹。

308
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:19,440
Now, according to Jimmy, the bank manager's leaving early on Tuesday, because it's his
现在，根据吉米的情报，银行经理周二会提前下班，因为那天是他

309
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,400
wedding anniversary.
的结婚纪念日。

310
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:26,840
He and the wife are having a romantic rendezvous in the country, so any packages delivered
他和妻子要在乡下浪漫约会，所以任何送到的包裹

311
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:31,400
will be left unopened in his office until he gets back late on Wednesday.
都会原封不动地放在他办公室里，直到他周三晚回来。

312
00:13:31,400 --> 00:13:35,240
Which gives us access to his office for at least 12 hours.
这样我们就有至少12小时可以进入他的办公室。

313
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:38,240
Okay Ralph, this is where you come in.
好的拉尔夫，这就是你出场的时候了。

314
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,240
Where are you?
你在哪儿？

315
00:13:39,240 --> 00:13:42,240
I'm standing right next to you, Sammy.
我就站在你旁边，萨米。

316
00:13:42,240 --> 00:13:46,080
Oh, sorry Sam, I'm in the box, right here, in that box.
哦，抱歉萨姆，我在箱子里，就在这儿，在那个箱子里。

317
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:49,400
And what do you do once I deliver you to the manager's office?
一旦我把你送到经理办公室，你做什么？

318
00:13:49,400 --> 00:13:54,840
I stay in the box until the bank is closed, and then I get out of the box.
我待在箱子里直到银行关门，然后我出来。

319
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,360
And then?
然后呢？

320
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,360
What next, Ralph?
接下来呢，拉尔夫？

321
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:00,120
Oh, for Pete's sake, this is never going to work.
哦，老天爷，这根本行不通。

322
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,320
Hey, give me a chance here, fellas.
嘿，给我个机会嘛，伙计们。

323
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:12,000
I crack the safe and then, then I take the money, and then I, um, I get back in the box.
我撬开保险柜，然后，然后拿走钱，然后我，呃，再回到箱子里。

324
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,640
Atta boy, Ralph.
好样的，拉尔夫。

325
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:17,320
In the morning I come back to the bank, say there's been a mix-up with the delivery I
早上我回到银行，说送货出了点差错，我

326
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:20,120
made and take the special package back here.
把那个特殊包裹拿回这里。

327
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:22,400
Alright, let's get some sleep.
好了，咱们睡会儿吧。

328
00:14:22,400 --> 00:14:27,360
It's a big day tomorrow, fellas.
明天是大日子，伙计们。

329
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:29,080
A perfect plan, Sammy!
完美的计划，萨米！

330
00:14:29,080 --> 00:14:31,440
It went off without a hitch!
一切顺利，毫无差错！

331
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:35,640
Let's open this up and get Ralph out of here so we can start counting the money.
咱们打开这个，把拉尔夫弄出来，好开始数钱。

332
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:39,280
Phew, I sure am glad to see you guys.
